---
---
<section class="section section--dark manifesto" aria-label="Our manifesto">
  <div class="container manifesto__grid">
    <div class="manifesto__left">
      <blockquote class="manifesto__quote reveal">
        <p class="display-xs">&ldquo;Every luxury travel guide is written by someone who visited once.<br/>We live here.&rdquo;</p>
        <footer class="manifesto__attrib">
          &mdash; Tim Hennig, General Manager, Boutique Hotel Matlai, Zanzibar
        </footer>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="manifesto__body reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="body-l">Beyond Paradise isn't built from press trips and sponsored itineraries. It's built from five years of living and working in one of the world's great luxury destinations — and knowing exactly who does it right.</p>
        <p class="body-m" style="margin-top:16px;color:var(--cream-65)">No hosted stays. No advertiser influence. Every lodge Tim or Kim visits, they pay for themselves.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="manifesto__right">
      <div class="manifesto__card glass reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <!-- Replace with Tim's portrait -->
        <div class="manifesto__photo" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1C1C21 0%,#2A7B8C22 100%);">
          <span class="manifesto__photo-label">Tim Hennig · Zanzibar, 2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="manifesto__card-body">
          <p class="label" style="color:var(--gold)">BEYOND PARADISE AFRICA</p>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--cream-65);margin-top:8px;">GM, Hotel Matlai · 5 years in East Africa · First-hand reviewer of 80+ luxury properties</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="manifesto__card glass reveal reveal-delay-3" style="border-color:rgba(74,171,184,0.25);">
        <div class="manifesto__card-body">
          <p class="label label--teal">BEYOND PARADISE ASIA</p>
          <p class="manifesto__kim-name">Kim</p>
          <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--cream-65);">Vietnamese, based in Zanzibar. First-hand knowledge of Hoi An, Hanoi, Ha Long Bay &amp; Hue.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.manifesto__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}
.manifesto__left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px; padding-top: 20px; }
.manifesto__quote { border: none; }
.manifesto__quote p {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px);
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--cream);
  line-height: 1.35;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.manifesto__attrib { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gold); }

.manifesto__right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
.manifesto__card { border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; }
.manifesto__photo {
  height: 280px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  padding: 16px;
}
.manifesto__photo-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--cream-38); }
.manifesto__card-body { padding: 20px 22px 24px; }
.manifesto__kim-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
  font-size: 28px;
  color: var(--cream);
  margin: 8px 0 8px;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .manifesto__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  .manifesto__right { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .manifesto__card { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }
}
</style>
